Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: Anryze Tokensale is successfully completed! We would like to announce our tokensale successfully completed!  ✨Thank you for your participation!✨ ✨✨Thank you for supporting our project! ✨✨  Next step will be tokens’ distribution. You ll get instructions to your email how to connect your Waves wallet with your Anryze account. Here it is published as well. INSTRUCTIONS FOR WITHDRAWAL RYZ TOKENS To receive RYZ tokens, please follow 4 steps:  1. Create a Waves account using one of these apps: ● Chrome app: https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/wavesliteapp/kfmcaklajknfekomaflnhkjjkcjabogm ● Web wallet: https://waveswallet.io ● Android mobile app: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.wavesplatform.wallet ● IOS mobile app: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/waves-wallet/id1233158971?mt=8 If you have any questions regarding WAVES Wallet you may contact http://support.wavesplatform.com.  2. Back up your SEED.  You must write this down, save it on another device (e.g. USB) or otherwise store it safely. Without your seed you may ultimately lose access to your Waves account.  3. Input your Waves address into “address“ field in the dashboard.  4. Confirm the address with the link sent to your email.  ATTENTION! Please do not use addresses of exchanges.  After RYZ token’s verification you can trade it on DEX exchange. Also it will be tradable on Tidex exchange and Kuna.  Soon some other exchanges will add RYZ token as well. It will be announced later. Bounties will be count and distribtuted at the beginning of the next week. If you have any questions, you can always write in our groups or to support@anryze.com  ✨We appreciate your support!✨  Join Anryze team Telegram chat and ask your questionshttps://t.me/anryze_tokensale For more details https://tokensale.anryze.com

Author: enigmatical
Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: It will be available to anyone who has access to the blockchains network that's why it is decentralized. The decentralized network consists of three components - computing powers (virtual machines of miners with a recognition program), a nodes with a distributed table(DHT) and a Waves blockchain for payment.

Author: khroma
Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: Can you explain how this works?

Author: enigmatical
Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: The system consists of users and miners. Users are those who want to rent computIng power for transcription and pay for that. Miners, on the other side, lease their power and get paid for it. User app detects suitable miner automatically through DHT and sends a request using the p2p link. After setting up the connection, user app forms the smart contract between User and Miner. When all confirmations received, payment goes to the miner and the second Smart Contract responsible for the commission of the system gets it. This contract accumulates transaction of the 24h period and then calculates the amount of the reward for each wallet based on the proportion of tokens held. Please refer to the whitepaper for more details

Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: Anryze recognizes speech by taking the waveform, split it on utterances by silences then try to recognize what is being said in each utterance. Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: Hi! Hope somebody can reply I wanted to know how will Anryze's decentralised system work?

Author: enigmatical
Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: The decentralized network consists of three components - computing powers (virtual machines of miners with a recognition program), a nodes with a distributed table (DHT) and a Waves blockchain for payment.The system consists of users and miners. Users are those who want to rent computing power for transcription and pay for that. Miners, on the other side, lease their power and get paid for it. User app detects suitable miner automatically through DHT and sends a request using the p2p link. After setting up the connection, user app forms the smart contract between User and Miner. When all confirmations received, payment goes to the miner and the second Smart Contract responsible for the commission of the system gets it. This contract accumulates transaction of the 24h period and then calculates the amount of the reward for each wallet based on the proportion of tokens held. These calculations are expensive and can not be used for each simple transaction in the system. While user uploads the file to the plugin, he receives the cost of transcription based on the duration of the audio and current price. In order to find the miner, the program would connect to DHT node or be that node and detects the suitable option (based on apparent capacities criteria). After that, it will send requests via p2p connection to the miner and receive confirmation of the readiness. For more details, you can refer to the white paper from tokensale.anryze.com

Author: Vladdirescu87
Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: Anryze, a distributed speech recognition platform, demonstrates the way in which blockchain technology allows grassroots users to become individual providers rather than relying on large companies for service provision.  The tendency of history has been one of increased centralisation. Ever since humans started living together in large numbers, prompted by the development of crop farming and animal husbandry, government and governance have naturally developed in one direction. Concentration of power – political, economic, military, administrative – has been the default state. The direction of travel may periodically be reversed, but such events tend to be unusual, and often sudden and violent: the fall of an empire, the death of a dictator, the collapse of a corporation.  Read the full article: https://coinidol.com/speech-to-text-platform-heralds-power-shift-of-blockchain/

Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: The cost depends on the recording time, each minute of the processed audio is equated to a token. We use the market price model, so the current cost of a minute will depend on transcription demand and mining supply in a system and also on token demand and supply on the crypto exchange. Initially, the rate will be 2:1 (two minutes for one token) and 1:0,02 (one token for $0,02).

Author: anryze
Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: The standard way in which Anryze recognises speech is as follows. We take the waveform, split it into segments (‘utterances’) on the basis of the silences between them, and then try to interpret what is being said in each utterance. To do that we want to take all possible combinations of words and try to match them with the audio, selecting the best matching combination.  Read our blog for details https://medium.com/anryze/the-challenges-of-speech-recognition-technology-48c6fed6260c

Author: Kibit
Title: [ANN][TOKENSALE][12|09] ••• Anryze: Distributed Speech Recognition Platform •••
Body: If we need to transcribe huge volume of audio, we should possess huge computational power and maintain powerful servers. We'are resolving this problem by building distributed computer network, where everyone can rent its available computational power to transcribe speech and to educate our neural network.  The token is used for transactions between all participants of the network from computational power suppliers to customers, who use this technology for their business purposes. All transactions within the system occur in tokens. Clients will create demand, as they pay by token for every transcribed minute
